sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_J100108
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:description: Riboswitch and GFP +High production of eCDM8
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: High promotor and low RBS (c-Dog). E. coli optimized caffeine demethylase with the same amino acid sequence as yCDM8 from Michener and Smolke (2012). Theophylline sensitive riboswitch mediates the production of GFP.
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: J100079 was ligated using Spe1 and J100105 using Xba1, so there is no scar between the two parts and EcoR1
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Erin McGuire

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_J100079
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: This part combines Riboswitch D (Part J100065) and superfolder GFP optimized for E. coli (Part J100070).
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Rebecca Evans

sbol:ComponentDefinition.dcterms:title: BBa_J100101
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableDescription: High promotor and high RBS (c-Dog). E. coli optimized caffeine demethylase with the same amino acid sequence as yCDM8 from Michener and Smolke (2012).
sbol:ComponentDefinition.sbh:mutableNotes: S05008 was ligated using Bsa1, so there is no scar between the two parts and Pst1
sbol:ComponentDefinition.dc:creator: Erin McGuire
